                                  <li>●	Garner Support from Friends</li>
                                  <li>●	Note Down the Instances of Bullying </li>
                                  <li>●	Subtly Extend a Helping Hand to a Victim </li>
                                  <li>●	Give Neutral Responses to Taunts </li>
                                  <li>●	Inform your Parents and a Teacher </li>
                                  <li>● Report Any Form of Violence Immediately </li>
                                  <li>●	Form Anti-Bullying Committees</li>
                                   
                                  	</ul> 
                                  
                              </p>
